<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>EduForge Edu - Question Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
      /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: white;
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Question Reply Notification</h1>
      <p>
        Hello <%= name %>,You have received a reply to your question in the
        Learly Education.
      </p>

      <p>
        A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title %>".
        Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the
        discussion.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any further questions or need assistance, please feel free
        to reply to the video section.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you for using our EduForge Education Website!</p>

      <p>Best Regards,</p>
      <p>The EduForge Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
